    | flag adds 1 lines: 1058612
    | flag removes 16 lines:   File: input.txt,   Size: 10586     	Blocks: 24         IO Block: 4096   regular file, Device: 254,0	Inode: 148638233   Links: 1, Access: (0644/-rw-r--r--)  Uid: ( 1000/mmontalbo)   Gid: (  100/   users), Access: 2026-05-14 12:40:44.576102500 -0700
    without flag:
        File: input.txt
